玛雅文明发祥的中美洲国家墨西哥、危地马拉、洪都拉斯和厄瓜多尔在各国最大的玛雅遗址举办各种活动，庆祝13伯克盾结束。2011年12月11日，[[恰帕斯州|恰帕斯州]]玛雅城镇{{tsl|en|Tapachula|塔帕丘拉}}启动了八英尺高数字钟，为13伯克盾结束倒计时<ref name="hindustantimes" />。2012年12月21日，墨西哥[[奇琴伊察|奇琴伊察]]和危地马拉[[蒂卡尔|蒂卡尔]]举行了盛大的活动<ref name=ChiItza>{{cite news|url=http://www.nacion.com/2012-12-21/AldeaGlobal/miles-llegan-a-chichen-itza-con-la-esperanza-de-una-nueva-era-mejor.aspx|title=Miles llegan a Chichén Itzá con la esperanza de una nueva era mejor|language=es|trans-title=Thousands arrive to Chichén Itzá with the hope of a new better era|agency=[[法新社|Agence France-Presse]]|work={{tsl|en|La Nación (Costa Rica)||La Nación (Costa Rica)}}|date=2012-12-21|access-date=2012-12-22|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121221202223/http://www.nacion.com/2012-12-21/AldeaGlobal/miles-llegan-a-chichen-itza-con-la-esperanza-de-una-nueva-era-mejor.aspx|archive-date=2012-12-21}}</ref><ref name=NYT122112>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/12/22/world/americas/doomsday-fizzles-but-many-hail-a-new-era.html|title=As Doomsday Flops, Rites in Ruins of Mayan Empire|author=Randal C. Archibold|work=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]|date=2012-12-21|access-date=2012-12-22|archive-date=2012-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121222013244/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/12/22/world/americas/doomsday-fizzles-but-many-hail-a-new-era.html}}</ref><ref name=Hff/>。厄瓜多尔{{tsl|en|Tazumal|塔祖马尔}}和洪都拉斯[[科潘|科潘]]也有盛大活动举行。这些在考古遗迹举行的玛雅祭祀活动，大多由[[萨满教|萨满]]和玛雅[[祭司|祭司]]在破晓时候主持<ref name=LN122112>{{cite news|url=http://www.nacion.com/2012-12-21/AldeaGlobal/mayas-guatemaltecos-inician-ceremonia-de-fuego-para-recibir-nueva-era.aspx|title=Mayas guatemaltecos inician ceremonia de fuego para recibir nueva era|language=es|trans-title=Guatemalan Mayans begin fire ceremony to welcome new era|agency=[[法新社|Agence France-Presse]]|work={{tsl|en|La Nación (Costa Rica)||La Nación (Costa Rica)}}|date=2012-12-21|access-date=2012-12-22|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121221230410/http://www.nacion.com/2012-12-21/AldeaGlobal/mayas-guatemaltecos-inician-ceremonia-de-fuego-para-recibir-nueva-era.aspx|archive-date=2012-12-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://latino.foxnews.com/latino/news/2012/12/21/salvadorenos-celebran-el-13-baktun-entre-danzas-ceremonias-y-deseos-de-paz/|title=Salvadoreños celebran el 13 Bʼaktun entre danzas, ceremonias y deseos de paz|language=es|trans-title=Salvadoreans commemorate the Bʼaktun 13 with dancing, ceremonials and wishes for peace|author=EFE|work=[[福斯新聞頻道|Fox News Latino]]|date=2012-12-22|access-date=2012-12-22|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130520070817/http://latino.foxnews.com/latino/news/2012/12/21/salvadorenos-celebran-el-13-baktun-entre-danzas-ceremonias-y-deseos-de-paz/|archive-date=2013-05-20}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.elheraldo.hn/Secciones-Principales/Vida/Turistas-invaden-Copan-Ruinas-en-cierre-del-13-baktun|title=Turistas invaden Copán Ruinas en cierre del 13 baktun|language=es|trans-title=Tourists invade the Copan Ruins for the end of the baktun 13|author=Gustavo Banegas|work=El Heraldo (Tegucigalpa)|date=2012-12-22|access-date=2012-12-22|archive-date=2013-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130922134702/http://www.elheraldo.hn/Secciones-Principales/Vida/Turistas-invaden-Copan-Ruinas-en-cierre-del-13-baktun}}</ref>。

